text: Kelly Michelle Lee Osbourne (born 27 October 1984, in London) is an English singer and actress. She is the daughter of the singer Ozzy Osbourne. Osborne is one of the co-presenters in the E! programme Fashion Police. She also presents a programme on BBC Radio 1 called The Surgery on Sunday evening. Her duet song with her father, singer Ozzy Osbourne, "Changes", received much praise. == Other websites == *The Official Kelly Osbourne Website *Kelly Osbourne at bbc.co.uk * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:English singers Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:Participants in American reality television series
